3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, snake
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, july, december
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, taxi
 1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 3. the person drinking water is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in july and the fan of pop##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in june and the owner of the snake##2
 7. the person driving the bike is between the person eating strawberry and the person drinking 7up##2
 8. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 9. the journalist is on the right of the fan of indie##1
10. the engineer is the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
